longs to the Schatten\n$p$-class $\\SSS_p(A^2_\\om)$ are also described. Furthermore, techniques\ndeveloped are applied to the study of the growth and the oscillation of\nanalytic solutions of (linear) differential equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2012 18:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-12"}
