c\nequation of state is determined under the conditions relevant to the interiors\nof magnetars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2012 19:07:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2013 20:45:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-02"}
